<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-2"></div>

<div class="newJob col-md-8">
  {{#if addNewJob}}
    <form>
      <h2 align="center">Post a New Job</h2>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="title">Job Title</label>
      {{input value=title id="title" class="form-control"}}

      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="from">From Destinaton</label>
      {{input value=from id="from" class="form-control"}}

      </div><div class="form-group">
        <label for="to">Destination</label>
      {{input value=to id="to" class="form-control"}}

    </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="amount">Proposed Amount</label>
      {{input value=amount id="amount" class="form-control"}}

      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="carryingDate">Date of Carrying</label>
      {{input value=date id="carryingDate" class="form-control"}}

      </div><div class="form-group">
        <label for="author">Customer's Name</label>
      {{input value=author id="author" class="form-control"}}

      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="phoneNumber">Phone Number</label>
      {{input value=phoneNumber id="phoneNumber" class="form-control"}}

      </div><div class="form-group">
        <label for="email">Email Address</label>
      {{input value=email id="email" class="form-control"}}

      </div>
    </form>

    <button  class= "btn-primary btn-lg" type="button" name="button" {{action 'saveJob'}}>Post New Job</button>

{{else}}
<h3>The Safari254 Advantage</h3>
<h4>Does any of these statements describe you?</h4>
<ul>
  <li>I have had terrible experiences finding a good transporter</li>
    <li>Most of the time my items have been crushed on the way</li>
      <li>I am always charged exhorbitantly</li>
        <li>I have no clue where to get a trusted transporter</li>
</ul>
<h4>Well, you have come to the right place. Safari254 gives you the following features</h4>
<ul>
<li>Trusted and approved drivers</li>
<li>You have variety of transport providers to choose from</li>
<li>Your feedback is welcome to improve our services</li>
</ul>
<button class="btn"{{action 'showJobForm'}}>Click here if you want to book a driver</button>
{{/if}}
</div>
<div class="col-md-2"></div>
</div>
